OL,4,CSocial care charges: Disabled and
OL,5,Cvulnerable adults hit by steep rises
OL,6, Disabled and vulnerable adults in
OL,7, England are being hit by a steep rise
OL,8, in the amount they have to pay towards
OL,9, their care, BBC News research reveals.
OL,11,FSome adults with learning disabilities
OL,12,Fare paying thousands of pounds extra a
OL,13,Fyear, with six councils doubling the
OL,14,Famount of money they receive.
OL,16,FIn half of 83 areas that responded to a
OL,17,FBBC request, bills across all users
OL,18,Fhave risen at least 10% over two years.
OL,20,FDirectors of council care services
OL,21,Fblame years of government funding cuts.
